    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Halved is a roguelike action RPG game with only 5 levels and 3 game modes, but innumerable possibilities for each run. Play as one of 5 characters and traverse the dangerous parts of the world with the help of the mysterious <i>Father of all Machines </i>against his rebel/tyrant son, <i>S.A.N.E.D.</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect powerful items and stack them to up, keeping a select few in between levels and converting the rest into health. Discover a unique ending with a certain character right after obliterating the final boss with possibly godlike power.</p>",
